metadata.name: COURage
metadata.description:
I am proud to present my first NFT "COURage". This is an exciting moment for me in my journey as a NFT collector and investor so far.

"COURage" is the result of my passion and curiosity, and I am confident that it shows all the intense emotions I have in this process. 

I am proud to be part of a growing community of web3 enthusiasts, artists and innovators who are pushing the boundaries of what is possible in this space for each of us. I am excited to see where this journey takes me.

So take a chance on "COURage" and join me on this exciting adventure. Probably, in just a few short months, I will look back with pride and a sense of accomplishment for taking the leap. This NFT is not just a digital asset, but a symbol of my commitment to creativity and innovation in this world.

I'm sure the courage will pay off.
